'''Preston Greenfield''' is a background character in ''[[Game of Thrones]]''. He is played by an unidentified extra and first mentioned by name in &quot;[[Two Swords]]&quot;. Ser Preston is a [[knight]] and a member of the [[Kingsguard]], defending King [[Joffrey Baratheon]] as he defended King [[Robert Baratheon]] before him.

sections.Biography:
===[[Season 1]]===
He was among the guards that attacked [[Eddard Stark]] when the [[Hand of the King]] attempts to arrest [[Cersei Lannister]], and take her children into his custody.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[You Win or You Die]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 4]]===

After Jaime returns to King's Landing, he goes over with Ser Meryn the placement of the Kingsguard members in defensive positions during Joffrey's wedding, and mentions Ser Preston.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Two Swords]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
